Context:
* The Community Worker (Accelerated) (C131) program is offered by George Brown College.
* To learn more about the program, register for an online information session or watch a previously recorded session. Contact Community Services at 416-415-5000, ext. 2185 or communityservices@georgebrown.ca, or Program Co-ordinator Farhia Abdi at fabdi7@georgebrown.ca to register.
* Application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and other information can be received by signing up on the website.
* The contact numbers for George Brown College are 416-415-2000 and TTY: 1-877-515-5559. The email address is ask.george@georgebrown.ca.
* The information on the website is subject to change without notice.
* George Brown College fee requirements must be verified by students.
